

This project is created to find joined spam groups of user and users' friend.
It's based on PHP CodeIgniter framework, so you need all php stack to run this.


To setup the project , you need to do following steps:

1.setup database
We use mysql to develope this,you could find the sql file in application/sql folder.

2.setup database setting

Please clone "application/config/database.php.sample.php" to
"application/config/database.php" and make sure you set it with right user name/pwd .
(More info: http://ellislab.com/codeigniter/user-guide/database/connecting.html )


It's now only for Traditional Chinese version ,
welcome to fork it and modify it.

The project is under CC-BY or you could discuss with TonyQ. :p

